# 将项目标记为中文项目
*.md linguist-language=Chinese
*.py linguist-language=Python
docs/*.md linguist-language=Chinese

# 文档文件标记为中文
README.md linguist-language=Chinese
CONTRIBUTING.zh-CN.md linguist-language=Chinese
游戏开发Excel配置表比较指南.md linguist-language=Chinese

# 确保中文文档被检测
*.md linguist-detectable=true
docs/ linguist-detectable=true